A \text{ totally bounded}
\;\iff\;
\forall\,\varepsilon > 0,\;
\exists\, n \in \mathbb{N},\;
\exists\, x_1, …, x_n \in X,\quad
A \subseteq \bigcup_{k=1}^n B_\varepsilon(x_k).
\]

